PUBLIC
public is the default modifier in kotlin.
public modifier is accessible from anywhere in the project
If no modifier is specified for the class, inteface, method, properties... the default one is public

PROTECTED
Protected modifier with a class or interface allow visbility to its class or subclass only
A protected declaration when overriden in its sublass becomes protected too unless it is explicitly changed
A protected monifire cannot be declared at the top

INTERNAL
The internal modifier makes the field visible inside the module only in which it is implemented

PRIVATE
A private modifier allows the declaration to only be accessible within the block in which properties, fields... are declared
A private package can ve accessible only within that specific file
The private modifier declaration does not allow access outside the scope.
